{"schema_version": "chunk_cache_v1", "source_file": "d:\\pycharmprojects\\finance_ai\\data\\raw\\financial_reports\\111.txt", "file_hash": "518664e20d5f1ac095ad2c2084603cb0", "metadata_hash": "1939344a8c81b9432876d3e24407cfa6", "signature": "{\"markdown_chunker\": \"hierarchy_recursive_v1\", \"max_chars\": 1200, \"normalization\": \"registry_driven_opencc_t2s\", \"overlap_chars\": 120, \"schema\": \"financial_pipeline_v2\"}", "chunks": [{"chunk_id": "9097cc75ba325236c121ef9ba5e9459f", "doc_id": "3915c5d63cd29ace0e00519742d834a8", "text": "整体来看，百度2025年财报呈现出AI转型成效显著但短期业绩承压的态势。长期战略上，公司通过AI云、自动驾驶等业务的突破，逐步构建起第二增长曲线，展现出技术积累向商业价值转化的潜力；但短期受传统业务收缩、资产减值等因素拖累，盈利指标出现较大波动，需关注现金流压力与市场竞争加剧带来的挑战。", "source_file": "D:\\PycharmProjects\\finance_ai\\data\\raw\\financial_reports\\111.txt", "page_start": 1, "page_end": 1, "section_path": "", "doc_type": "quarterly_results", "metadata": {"file_name": "111.txt", "company_id": "BIDU_baidu", "ticker": "BIDU", "company_name": "Baidu Inc", "doc_type": "quarterly_results", "report_period": "FY2025", "publish_date": "", "source_url": "local_file", "cninfo_detail_url": "", "language": "zh-Hans", "source_priority": "local", "text_normalization": "", "is_core_document": "true", "parse_status": "downloaded", "registry_hash": "518664e20d5f1ac095ad2c2084603cb0", "industry": "互联网搜索与AI", "source_file_hash": "518664e20d5f1ac095ad2c2084603cb0", "registry_metadata_hash": "1939344a8c81b9432876d3e24407cfa6", "chunk_cache_signature": "{\"markdown_chunker\": \"hierarchy_recursive_v1\", \"max_chars\": 1200, \"normalization\": \"registry_driven_opencc_t2s\", \"overlap_chars\": 120, \"schema\": \"financial_pipeline_v2\"}"}}, {"chunk_id": "b84b32b903cdd1b5e7dccd33c6ef9f83", "doc_id": "3915c5d63cd29ace0e00519742d834a8", "text": "一、财务核心数据", "source_file": "D:\\PycharmProjects\\finance_ai\\data\\raw\\financial_reports\\111.txt", "page_start": 1, "page_end": 1, "section_path": "", "doc_type": "quarterly_results", "metadata": {"file_name": "111.txt", "company_id": "BIDU_baidu", "ticker": "BIDU", "company_name": "Baidu Inc", "doc_type": "quarterly_results", "report_period": "FY2025", "publish_date": "", "source_url": "local_file", "cninfo_detail_url": "", "language": "zh-Hans", "source_priority": "local", "text_normalization": "", "is_core_document": "true", "parse_status": "downloaded", "registry_hash": "518664e20d5f1ac095ad2c2084603cb0", "industry": "互联网搜索与AI", "source_file_hash": "518664e20d5f1ac095ad2c2084603cb0", "registry_metadata_hash": "1939344a8c81b9432876d3e24407cfa6", "chunk_cache_signature": "{\"markdown_chunker\": \"hierarchy_recursive_v1\", \"max_chars\": 1200, \"normalization\": \"registry_driven_opencc_t2s\", \"overlap_chars\": 120, \"schema\": \"financial_pipeline_v2\"}"}}, {"chunk_id": "f9eae5a621cf24fe314ad51e02ded04a", "doc_id": "3915c5d63cd29ace0e00519742d834a8", "text": "营收利润双降：总营收1290.79亿元（同比-3.04%），归母净利润55.89亿元（同比-76.48%）。净利润下滑主因计提162亿元长期资产减值损失，若剔除该因素，Non-GAAP净利润为189亿元（同比-30%）。\n现金流压力显现：全年经营现金流-30.13亿元（同比减少242亿元），但下半年转正至39亿元，显示阶段性改善。\n二、业务重点突破", "source_file": "D:\\PycharmProjects\\finance_ai\\data\\raw\\financial_reports\\111.txt", "page_start": 1, "page_end": 1, "section_path": "", "doc_type": "quarterly_results", "metadata": {"file_name": "111.txt", "company_id": "BIDU_baidu", "ticker": "BIDU", "company_name": "Baidu Inc", "doc_type": "quarterly_results", "report_period": "FY2025", "publish_date": "", "source_url": "local_file", "cninfo_detail_url": "", "language": "zh-Hans", "source_priority": "local", "text_normalization": "", "is_core_document": "true", "parse_status": "downloaded", "registry_hash": "518664e20d5f1ac095ad2c2084603cb0", "industry": "互联网搜索与AI", "source_file_hash": "518664e20d5f1ac095ad2c2084603cb0", "registry_metadata_hash": "1939344a8c81b9432876d3e24407cfa6", "chunk_cache_signature": "{\"markdown_chunker\": \"hierarchy_recursive_v1\", \"max_chars\": 1200, \"normalization\": \"registry_driven_opencc_t2s\", \"overlap_chars\": 120, \"schema\": \"financial_pipeline_v2\"}"}}, {"chunk_id": "ba3406c578f912e45e4b98c8ea5b4768", "doc_id": "3915c5d63cd29ace0e00519742d834a8", "text": "AI业务占比超四成：AI相关收入400亿元（同比+48%），Q4占核心业务收入43%。其中：\nAI云基础设施收入198亿元（同比+34%），算力订阅收入增长143%；\nAI原生营销收入98亿元（同比+301%），依托文心大模型实现广告内容智能生成；\n自动驾驶（萝卜快跑）Q4订单340万次（同比+200%），覆盖全球26城，累计服务超2000万次。\n技术壁垒强化：文心大模型升级至5.0版本（参数量2.4万亿），昆仑芯启动港股上市，夯实AI全栈能力。\n三、风险与挑战\n\n传统业务持续收缩：搜索广告收入下滑拖累整体增速，用户时长面临短视频平台分流压力；\n盈利修复存疑：AI业务高投入导致销售成本同比+10%，毛利率承压；\n全球化竞争加剧：自动驾驶面临Waymo等技术竞争，AI云遭遇阿里云、华为云市场份额争夺。\n机构观点\n中泰证券认为“AI商业化拐点已至，维持增持评级”；摩根士丹利指出“短期盈利承压但技术储备领先，评级持股观望”；高盛强调“需关注昆仑芯分拆上市对估值体系的重构机会”。", "source_file": "D:\\PycharmProjects\\finance_ai\\data\\raw\\financial_reports\\111.txt", "page_start": 1, "page_end": 1, "section_path": "", "doc_type": "quarterly_results", "metadata": {"file_name": "111.txt", "company_id": "BIDU_baidu", "ticker": "BIDU", "company_name": "Baidu Inc", "doc_type": "quarterly_results", "report_period": "FY2025", "publish_date": "", "source_url": "local_file", "cninfo_detail_url": "", "language": "zh-Hans", "source_priority": "local", "text_normalization": "", "is_core_document": "true", "parse_status": "downloaded", "registry_hash": "518664e20d5f1ac095ad2c2084603cb0", "industry": "互联网搜索与AI", "source_file_hash": "518664e20d5f1ac095ad2c2084603cb0", "registry_metadata_hash": "1939344a8c81b9432876d3e24407cfa6", "chunk_cache_signature": "{\"markdown_chunker\": \"hierarchy_recursive_v1\", \"max_chars\": 1200, \"normalization\": \"registry_driven_opencc_t2s\", \"overlap_chars\": 120, \"schema\": \"financial_pipeline_v2\"}"}}]}